Package examservice

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVParser
    This class handles the parsing of a CSV file, The CSV file is read line by line, from which data is pulled into a DataEntry type (see class), The class is meant to run by passing a file on construction, and then calling getDB to get a type ExamDB (see class).
    DataEntry
    This class is 'an entry' of a CSV file line, it has all fields necessary to create an object with all the available information from one line of a CSV file
    ExamDB
    This class holds a List of DataEntries, this is the main database class, an object of this class can hold all information from a CSV file
    ExamService
    Top of class - Only handles instantiating new GUI
    GUI
    This class is the main GUI for the program.
